            . I am a carpenter. I was standing opposite Lorton's shop, and saw Tilley take these trousers<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182704050027"></xptr>down, and give them to Parker, who was in his company; I secured Tilley, and gave him to a man to hold; I then ran, and saw Parker stopped; he threw the trousers down- I picked them up, and took both the prisoners to the shop - they denied the charge.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
